{"tid":426720,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁古怪？】有隻股今年勁升3倍 CFO唔撈 核數師辭任","createTime":"2017-10-07T01:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T01:13:22.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e298e6977ac65b93854a4059cad2e285608d8e51","tid":426720,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171006/large/1507288266_c140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171006%2Flarge%2F1507288266_c140.jpg&h=5b17082b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n珩灣科技（1523）宣佈，德勤已辭任該公司的核數師，自2017年10月4日起生效，原因為該公司未能與德勤就今年度的核數費用達成共識。珩灣科技為SD-WAN路由器供應商，年初至今股價勁升3.35倍，市值19.3億元。<br />\n<br />\n該公司早前有財務總監吳舜瑛辭任，由謝嘉熙接任，9月27日生效。<br />\n<br />\n公司建議委任安永作為其核數師以填補德勤辭任之後的臨時空缺，安永目前正在辦理與建議委任有關的若干內部程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57299515&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57299515%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171006&d=NhYFn%2Fa2OU0mLL9Pl%2FauMm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3f361c4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57299515%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171006&h=483b067a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57299515&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171006</a>"}]}